## ğŸ”¬ How to Use
1. Pick a sketch based on what you want to test (line following, PID tuning, encoder reading).
2. Upload to the Nano and open Serial Monitor (9600 baud).
3. Observe sensor outputs, motor speeds, and PID corrections.
4. Tweak constants and reâ€‘upload to refine behavior.
5. Save promising results or log data for offline analysis.

